Note: We do not offer drop-in advising hours on Career Fair Days. Refer to the Upcoming Events Calendar.  Monday, Tuesday, Thursday: 1:00 pm - 4:00 pm.


Wednesday & Friday: 10 am - 1:00  pm.      Resource Center
Drop in any time at the Career Services Office (Student Services Building) to utilize our printed and/or computer resources for employer research, job search, or to work on your resume and cover letters 	Monday – Friday: 8:30 am - 5:00 pm  Monday – Friday: 8:30 am - 5:00 pm.       Scheduled Individual Advising Appointments If you would like to meet with a Career Adviser, please contact our office by phone at (312) 996-2300 .  Appointments must be scheduled at least one business day in advance.  Monday – Friday:  9:00 am – 4:00 pm.               About    Back to main content           Hours & Location    Our Services    Contact Us    Staff Directory     Career Peer Mentors      Other Career Centers    Newsletters & Recorded Webinars    Frequently Asked Questions                  UIC Logo        Career Services         Students    Career Planning Guide    Make an Appointment    FAQs      Employers    Post a Position    UICcareers.com      Campus Partners    Campus Partners    Program/Workshop Request Forms        Footer Menu    Career Programs and Events    UICcareers    UIC Student Employment Office         Contact   Suite 3050 1200 West Harrison Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-2300  Fax: (312) 413-0383  careerservices@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 